round-end-system-round-restart-eta-announcement-carp = Round will restart in {$time} {$units}...
  { $eorg ->
    [true] EORG (End-Of-Round Griefing) has been temporarily allowed.
    Roleplay rules are no longer enforced, feel free to go ham.
    *[false] EORG (End-Of-Round Griefing) is NOT allowed.
    Roleplay rules still apply, so make sure to follow them.
    Time until restart has been extended, enjoy post-round RP!
  }
